BIG ANNOUNCEMENT & A FAVOR
 As I look back on my 70 years of life, I am compelled to create something that lives BEYOND me and continues to serve all of you. Along the way I’ve picked up much of life’s secrets, knowledge and experience that I only wish I’d known sooner. 

Today, It’s become my mission and purpose to share my life of knowledge and experience with you. Right now I’m in the process of working with an amazing team to create a wide variety of courses and training materials on everything from How To Master Your Speaking Voice, How to focus and Win Your Mornings, How to add years to your life, How To Learn My Songs on the Piano, and so much more. 
 
But right now I need YOUR help. Will you comment below and tell me what you want me to teach?

What would you want my mentorship on? What are the skills, habits or tactics that, if you could quickly master them, would lift you up and move you forward in your life? Will you please comment below and let me know?.... and then I can get busy creating the teachings that’ll be of most value to you. 

Thank you for your time. I’m excited to see your responses!

Here's a better video about my latest mission. 
I will be guided by your ideas and your comments! Thanks. JT.
